data.text:
Bob Franklin and Bev Killick will blast their way onto the stage in this hilarious one night performance. BOLD, REAL & ENERGETIC this duo will have you in stitches during the comedy show of the year!

Details: Tickets cost $75 per person, which includes a two course meal and show. The Auditorium doors will open at 5:30pm for a 6:00pm meal and the show will begin at 8:00pm. Individual seats and tables of 10 are available for purchase. If you have any questions please email our Events Department at functions@bribiersl.com.au. To purchase tickets head to ‘SHOP’ on the Bribie RSL website or pop into Reception.
